254
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:32,876
Her father took off when she was a year
old and has only seen her twice since.

255
00:17:32,985 --> 00:17:34,384
He's a jerk.

256
00:17:35,521 --> 00:17:37,614
Well, at least she has you.

257
00:17:38,157 --> 00:17:42,025
And your mom, which is great for you
because you have a built- in babysitter.

258
00:17:42,127 --> 00:17:44,118
- Yes and no.
- Yeah?

259
00:17:44,229 --> 00:17:46,891
She's agoraphobic, so...

260
00:17:48,300 --> 00:17:51,633
Agoraphobic?
Like she can't leave the house?

261
00:17:51,737 --> 00:17:53,864
- Yeah.
- Oh wow, that's tough.

262
00:17:56,041 --> 00:17:58,339
How long has she been like that?

263
00:17:58,744 --> 00:18:01,542
- It's been about 15 years.
- Wow.

264
00:18:02,247 --> 00:18:05,045
- Not a second date story.
- Yeah. Okay.

265
00:18:06,051 --> 00:18:08,076
So, where are we going?

266
00:18:08,687 --> 00:18:12,054
We are going that way.

267
00:18:18,564 --> 00:18:20,031
Oh, my gosh.

268
00:18:21,533 --> 00:18:23,626
- I love this Ferris wheel.
- Yeah.

269
00:18:23,735 --> 00:18:25,896
- I thought they were gonna tear it down.
- They were.

270
00:18:26,004 --> 00:18:29,462
I bought it from the city and I restored it,
then I donated it back to them.

271
00:18:29,575 --> 00:18:32,373
Couldn't stand the thought of it just
sitting in some dump, somewhere.

272
00:18:32,478 --> 00:18:34,207
Used to ride it all the
time when I was a kid.

273
00:18:34,313 --> 00:18:36,247
- You kidding? So did I.
- What?

274
00:18:36,348 --> 00:18:38,145
- Do you remember the guy who ran it?
- Benny.

275
00:18:38,250 --> 00:18:39,581
- Benny.
- Benny.

276
00:18:39,685 --> 00:18:40,811
And he had a glass eye.

277
00:18:40,919 --> 00:18:43,217
- Yeah, and neither of them matched.
- No.

278
00:18:43,322 --> 00:18:44,653
Appetizer?

279
00:18:45,390 --> 00:18:46,857
Cotton candy.

280
00:18:47,392 --> 00:18:49,656
- Thank you, sir.
- You're welcome.

281
00:18:49,761 --> 00:18:51,023
Oh, dude.

282
00:18:52,064 --> 00:18:53,998
I'm sorry, Bill. Can I have one, too?

283
00:18:54,099 --> 00:18:55,930
- Here we are.
- Thanks.

284
00:18:57,236 --> 00:18:58,430
